{"type": "article", "id": 19613, "title": "实木书桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-24T07:40:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115037YeTSKPiGDFNljLk7.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这张实木书桌来自二黑木作，采用卯榫技术，上面没有开线圈或者设计开关，只有三个简单的小抽屉。设计者想借此让人回归到读书时代单纯的写字状态。抽屉的长宽相同，但高度不一致，三者可以自由交换顺序。桌腿的侧面连接了两根铜棒，可以挂上书包或图纸。有樱桃木和黑胡桃两种材料，售价 4100 元，<a href=\"http://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a230r.1.14.14.c9Hv87&amp;id=524801503322&amp;ns=1&amp;abbucket=4#detail\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115035gTL2m39sA1DFkRwn.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115036idBVaXqx8Te1khYn.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021150363yhAwQ9fxHnGYUE6.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"719\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115037yugUaHpd2sChSt6o.jpg\" width=\"433\" height=\"646\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49191686\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n"}